Policy_Text_EN: travel insurance covers trip cancellations lost luggage emergency medical expenses traveling abroad
Policy_Text_FR: lassurance voyag couvr annulatier voyage perte bagage frais mdical durgence ltranger
Policy_Text_ES: seguro viaje cubrir cancelación viaje prdida equipaje gasto mdico emergencia extranjero
Summarized_Text: Covers travel risks such as cancellations, lost luggage, and medical expenses.
French_Translation: assurance voyage couvre les annulations de voyage bagages perdus frais médicaux d'urgence voyage à l'étranger
Spanish_Translation: seguro de viaje cubre cancelaciones de viaje perdido equipaje gastos médicos de emergencia viajar al extranjero

Policy_Text_EN: home insurance protects fire theft natural disasters coverage includes structure personal belongings
Policy_Text_FR: lassurance habitation protge contre lincendie vol catastrophe naturel couvertur inclure structure effet personnel
Policy_Text_ES: seguro hogar proteger incendio robo desastre natural cobertura incluir estructura pertenencia personal
Summarized_Text: Protects home structure and belongings from risks like fire and theft.
French_Translation: l'assurance habitation protège le vol d'incendie la couverture des catastrophes naturelles comprend la structure des effets personnels
Spanish_Translation: seguro de vivienda protege robo de incendios cobertura desastres naturales incluye estructura pertenencias personales

Policy_Text_EN: home insurance protects fire theft natural disasters coverage includes structure personal belongings
Policy_Text_FR: lassurance habitation protge contre lincendie vol catastrophe naturel couvertur inclure structure effet personnel
Policy_Text_ES: seguro hogar proteger incendio robo desastre natural cobertura incluir estructura pertenencia personal

Policy_Text_EN: life insurance ensures financial security beneficiaries case policyholders death optional riders available disability coverage
Policy_Text_FR: lassurance vie assurer scurit financire bnficiaire cas dc titulaire police option supplmentaire disponible couvertur dinvalidit
Policy_Text_ES: seguro vida garantizar seguridad financiero beneficiario caso fallecimiento titular plizar opción adicional disponible cobertura discapacidad
Summarized_Text: Offers financial support for beneficiaries in case of policyholder’s death.
French_Translation: l'assurance vie assure la sécurité financière des bénéficiaires cas de souscripteurs décès cavaliers optionnels disponible couverture d'invalidité
Spanish_Translation: seguro de vida asegura beneficiarios de seguridad financiera asegurados asegurados asegurados fallecimientos residentes opcionales cobertura de discapacidad disponible

Policy_Text_EN: health insurance policy provides coverage hospitalization surgeries prescribed medications preexisting conditions may require additional evaluation
Policy_Text_FR: police dassuranc maladie couvr lhospitalisation chirurgier mdicament prescrire condition prexistante pouvoir ncessiter valuation supplmentair
Policy_Text_ES: plizar seguro salud cubrir hospitalizacin ciruga medicamento recetado condición preexistent poder requerir evaluacin adicional
Summarized_Text: Provides medical coverage including hospital visits and prescriptions.
French_Translation: La police d'assurance-maladie prévoit la couverture des hospitalisations Les médicaments prescrits pour les maladies préexistantes peuvent nécessiter une évaluation supplémentaire.
Spanish_Translation: póliza de seguro médico proporciona cobertura cirugías de hospitalización medicamentos prescritos condiciones preexistentes pueden requerir evaluación adicional
